# Complete Implementation: AI Prompt Generator with Gemini 2.5 Flash & Google Search

**Date:** May 11, 2026
**Model:** Gemini 2.5 Flash
**Features:** Real-time Google Search Grounding, JSON Mode, 400-character hard limits

